                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> His friends offered me the money two or three days—I said I could not take it—they called me into a public-house, and offered me 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I said, "No, it is too late," and then they brought it and left it with a woman—I would not take it—I gave it back to the woman—I was sober when he took it.</p>
